</span></p><p class="sc-bfhwqR jqvVoJ pf-476_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-fmzxHC hSXinz pf-475_"><strong><a href="https://nopr.niscpr.res.in/bitstream/123456789/24664/1/IJFTR%2029%284%29%20483-492.pdf" target="_blank"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"></span></a></strong><a href="https://www.statista.com/topics/9288/fashion-e-commerce-worldwide/" target="_blank"></a><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"></span><em>The era of excuses is over: we must either commit to genuine sustainability or become just another chapter in the story of fast fashion that forgot its footprint</em>
<br>

</span></p><img alt="t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp__PID:ee80cd59-b9b5-43c4-9c9d-c387190f3be0" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0550/2880/9974/files/t-shirt-in-biodegradable-packaging.webp?v=1743176243&width=2048 2048w" fetchPriority="low" decoding="async" loading="lazy" style="--pf-image-ratio:1.4990006662225184" width="4500" height="3002" sizes="75vw" data-pf-type="Image4" class="sc-dWZrec jpHayX pf-212_" store="[object Object]"/></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-sm-hide pf-hide" style="--c-xs:3;--c-sm:2;--c-md:6;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-bkSTSn hpQOMO pf-235_ pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kRRxPL kSaugo pf-236_ pf-heading-1-h3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><strong>Glossary<span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);">keywords</span></strong><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);"></span><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);"></span></span></h3><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-246_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Biodegradable Materials:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Substances that decompose naturally without harming ecosystems (e.g., plant-based polymers).



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-242_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Circular Economy:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Model focused on eliminating waste through reuse, recycling, and closed-loop systems.
</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-254_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Consumer Backlash:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Resistance to price hikes for sustainable products, forcing brands to balance ethics and affordability.

   



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-238_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Executive Order 13834:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Trump-era policy (2018) reversing Obama’s limits on federal single-use plastics, prioritizing cost over sustainability.



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-248_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Extended Producer Responsibility (EPR):</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Policies requiring manufacturers to manage recycling or disposal of their products.

   



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-244_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Fast Fashion:  </strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);"> Low-cost, rapidly produced clothing with high environmental and social costs.









</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-256_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Greenwashing:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Misleading claims about environmental benefits to appeal to eco-conscious consumers.

   



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-250_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>QR Codes:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Scannable codes linking to sustainability certifications or supply-chain transparency data.

   



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-240_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Single-Use Plastics:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Disposable plastics (e.g., bags, packaging) linked to pollution; targeted by state bans despite federal rollbacks.

   



</span></p><p class="sc-knuQPt cmQWaw pf-252_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(61, 74, 79);"><span style="color: rgb(196, 135, 74);"><strong>Supply-Chain Partnerships:</strong><br></span></span><span style="color: rgb(43, 54, 56);">Collaborations to secure ethical materials and withstand regulatory/tariff disruptions.

   



